{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<div style=\"background-color:#000000; text-align:center; vertical-align: middle; padding:10px 0;text-color:black\">\n<h1>The Mindful Way</h1>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background-color:#ffgggg; text-align:center; vertical-align: middle; padding:0px 0;text-color:black\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;overflow:hidden;padding:1px 1px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;overflow:hidden;padding:1px 1px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-0lax{text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n<table class=\"tg\">\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-0lax\"><h4><a href= \"/\">Home</a></h4></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-0lax\"><h4><a href= \"/poems\">Poems</a></h4></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-0lax\"><h4><a href= \"/blogs\">Blogs</a></h4></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-0lax\"><h4><a href =\"/contact-us\">Contact us</a></h4></th>\n  </tr>\n</thead>\n</table>\n</div>\n<br>\n<p>Mindfulness is a way of life and the principles of mindfulness can be applied to each and every living moment.</p>\n<p>This website is dedicated to sharing knowledge, experiences and thoughts about living life <i>The Mindful Way.</i></p>\n<p>Here's a <a href=\"/poems/the-mindful-way\">short poem</a> that provides a perspective on a mindful way of life.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"May 25, 2020","slug":"/","title":"Home"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/"}}}